  "date": "2025-09-18 03:11:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5cc5fca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUAJBEQib9WgoX6EeRoM4feiccjicAC2aj9QxVXguMnibbCn66o0IkEWKl7g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">当GPT-5第一次被写进数学论文，舆论瞬间炸开。有人惊呼「AI 数学家诞生」，有人却冷静提醒：它只是把熟悉的工具快速拼接。于是，一个新的问题被摆到台前：这究竟是科研的加速器，还是博士培养的绊脚石？</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayqt47y98\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfayqt4xs91\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">9月初，一篇挂在arXiv的论文在学界扔下一颗炸弹——GPT-5被写进了数学研究成果里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayqpwn1bxn\"><span leaf=\"\">研究者在文中公开写道：GPT-5在他们的实验中完成了一项此前从未解决的数学工作，并将结果直接纳入正式稿件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505142145\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7721139430284858\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"667\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"446\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5b0ee64&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUEXEriasJuChGkurEZN6ChqdvqdGbHTlJwBC4PQUIYxgYz4jVFdYw4eQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayqpwnblu\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是大型语言模型首次以「定理贡献者」的身份出现在数学研究论文中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayqpwnyqo\"><span leaf=\"\">论文所涉及的，正是Malliavin–Stein框架下的一个核心难题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">GPT-5第一次写进数学论文</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayren41kxf\"><span leaf=\"\">在数学研究里，「第四矩定理」是一块基础又棘手的拼图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayren41eb4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">它最初由Nualart和Peccati提出，用来判断某类随机变量是否收敛到正态分布。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayren4fuj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这个定理长期存在一个「缺口」：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayren418y8\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">它只能告诉你「会不会收敛」，却没法量化「收敛有多快」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayren4sgp\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队选择把这个缺口抛给GPT-5。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayren4gka\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们的问题很直接：在Malliavin–Stein框架下，能否把第四矩定理的「定性收敛」升级成「定量收敛」，给出明确的速度界限？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayren5nnc\"><span leaf=\"\">GPT-5 给出的答案令人意外。它推导出一个全新的收敛速度结论：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505141993\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2907608695652174\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"736\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"736\" data-height=\"214\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"163\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=815fd851&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUDthZtTeibVr6tWhybktm93FEhndrZCcXExHB5O7JYGyibq34DalUdVFA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">&nbsp;GPT-5推导出的新定理：第四矩定理首次有了明确的收敛速度，被原封不动收进论文</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrjo917s0\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，它证明了：如果第四矩逐渐逼近高斯分布的数值，那么收敛的速度也能被清晰刻画。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrjo91785\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一结果的意义不只在于解决了一个空白点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrjo91b2f\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">对数学研究者而言，收敛速度往往决定了定理能否真正应用到复杂模型里，比如高维随机场、金融数据的极值分析、甚至物理中的随机过程模拟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrjo9pyd\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">此前只能笼统地说「会收敛」，现在有了定量边界，很多应用才有了可操作性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrjo966d\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">更重要的是，这个过程不是研究团队「替GPT-5美化」，而是直接把它的推导纳入正式成果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrjo921su\"><span leaf=\"\">这是大型语言模型第一次以「定理贡献者」的身份，进入数学研究论文的正文部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-PUrSdMyzto5Y8axYpBLc7Ikwnxe&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">不是单挑</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-PUrSdMyzto5Y8axYpBLc7Ikwnxe&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">而是「教授+AI」的组合拳</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtanahs\"><span leaf=\"\">外界看到GPT-5被写进论文，很容易联想到「AI能独立解决数学难题」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtanf4e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但真相远远没有那么简单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtan18l6\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">GPT-5 一上来就写出了定理陈述，看似逻辑完整，但在关键环节 Cov(Y², Z²) 的推导上用了错误公式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtan23q5\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果不被及时发现，这个错误会直接毁掉整个证明。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505141994\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2556818181818182\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"704\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"704\" data-height=\"180\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"144\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ecf303a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUs7NV8dyR6oCiaCP2Mz55ItDcVFzPCunEKow89UEUBo8XicseYZZwL5yQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtan11ce\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者追问：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtan2wq\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Can you check your formula for Cov(Y², Z²) and provide me with the details?</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtan1aae\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">GPT-5乖乖给出细节解释，但仍然错了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505141995\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583634175691937\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"831\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"831\" data-height=\"464\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=daa89e3b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUgMGQN8o6JMJEsT9bZgbIGwsjzP2LDbj67CvFFRF9A9OUH5QvBc8EtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtantwk\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者干脆直接指出：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtan1uxq\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">I think you are mistaken in claiming that (p+q)!‖u⊗̃v‖² = p!q!‖u‖²‖v‖².</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtan137u\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">GPT-5这才承认之前的推理是假的，并调整思路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505141996\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7484197218710493\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"791\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"791\" data-height=\"592\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"42