\"663\" style=\"width:559px;height:387px;\" data-width=\"667\" data-height=\"479\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUXZqFrd2ycLLBMT7ibFsmIbsKbPrl5PkmZWfetCmMj9nQCFq5Ant3Sgg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"663.4395017793594\" data-cropy2=\"459.30427046263344\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"404\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7edbaa2e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUbiabcRulW6ffmepNKJoCavibmaGMsEy3dtxFFfcCCeAreq2GPkZeMicQg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrwhocgw\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfayrwi33se\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Mollick：GPT-5 Pro能做新数学，但必须在教授引导下</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfayrtanwdm\"><span leaf=\"\">这不是AI单挑，而是教授+AI的组合拳。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-O2LYdYuqgoXNUExpDi8cxk7OnXq&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">外界惊呼，内行冷静</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk21pu\"><span leaf=\"\">当GPT-5被写进论文的消息传开，许多圈外人第一反应是「历史性时刻」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gkars\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">8月20日，微软研究员Sébastien Bubeck在X上发了一条贴子：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk24ke\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">他 GPT-5 Pro去解一个凸优化领域的公开问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk1r4y\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">几分钟内，GPT-5把一个经典界限从1/L1/L1/L提升到了1.5/L1.5/L1.5/L。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505141998\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5959595959595959\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"594\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"594\" data-height=\"354\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"335\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1efa4cb0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUyQ4nHecaR2XM1Yq1ialxq8OKChsOHYTZgMnrdPjMib6R39ibOfa6CQRfQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505142000\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6123966942148761\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1210\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1210\" data-height=\"741\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"344\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9b40fcbb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUcEbuRsBssxl9wk2g3uZMP4X1Q7S9L2CFY2lScPLH9CUQV34tWjib0hA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gkl0\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">听上去像是枯燥的数学符号，为什么会引起如此轰动？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk1hys\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在凸优化里，1/L代表算法能达到的一个收敛速度上限，这个上限直接决定了算法跑得有多快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gkyki\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者们早已习惯把它当作定律，但GPT-5在几分钟内就给出了更紧的界限：1.5/L。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk1n4g\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，如果正确，它等于在数学上「加速」了整个领域里一大类算法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk1eva\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这条帖子迅速引爆社交媒体，被很多人视为AI数学家时代的开幕时刻。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk1ihc\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，数学界内部的解读则冷静得多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk1hgp\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">优化专家Ernest Ryu的评论道：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk15qd\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">GPT-5给出的这个展示主要依赖于一个早已为专家熟知的工具——Nesterov定理……一位有经验的研究人员也能在几个小时内得到等价的结果。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfays4gk21i5\"><span leaf=\"\">也就是说，在外界看来是「几分钟完成的突破」，在内行眼中其实是「熟悉工具的快速复用」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-JkJAd4WYvocwXbxk8bscDyDTnUe&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">是科研加速器，还是博士的绊脚石？</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr6g0a\"><span leaf=\"\">GPT-5被写进论文，看上去像是一台科研加速器，但作者在结尾却写下了不小的担忧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr61pc9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究人员发现，GPT-5最擅长的，其实是把已有的工具快速拼接成结果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr66v6\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">技术上没错，可缺少真正的原创性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr61wzi\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果未来越来越多这样的「拼图式研究」涌入学界，文献可能会被海量的「正确但平庸」的成果淹没，真正有突破性的工作更难脱颖而出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr6fw3\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">更需要让人警惕的，是博士生的成长路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr61nge\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">按照传统节奏，他们要靠反复阅读、尝试、犯错，慢慢培养研究直觉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr6nqk\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但如果AI可以随时生成技术正确的推导，这些至关重要的试错环节就会被跳过。论文里写得很直白：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr6tif\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果学生过度依赖人工智能……他们可能会失去发展这些基本技能的必要机会。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr61dus\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种担忧并非杞人忧天。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr61hq5\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI研究员Noam Brown也在公开场合提醒：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfaysv3s225q\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505141999\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43093093093093093\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"666\" height=\"280\" style=\"width: 100%;background-color: transparent;\" width=\"662\" data-width=\"666\" data-height=\"287\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"242\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d50aa48f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb25gBfwhFll9ua8iaribRKPbUVtZXyEvUlrXKXnFheJicyvP8bWA59UwTpqnmjAnAAOGUC3agTWXkDqw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr65ix\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">换句话说，GPT-5已经能产出新定理，但它会把科研变成「快餐流水线」，还是推动人类进入新一轮知识爆炸？答案没有人敢保证。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr61b3z\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">从Bubeck的凸优化案例，到Malliavin–Stein定理的定量化突破，GPT-5已经不再是实验室里的玩具，而是真正出现在学术论文的正文里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr6jew\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">它能生成定理，推导证明，甚至在教授引导下完成整套研究流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr62pk\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但问题也随之而来：当「正确但平庸」的结果可以大规模复制，原创突破会不会被淹没？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr6yzq\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">当博士生最重要的试错与摸索环节被 AI跳过，学术训练会不会失去根基？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr6ko7\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">未来几年，AI 在科研中扮演的角色，也许会比任何人想象得更快、更激烈地发生变化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfaysbr61ev3\"><span leaf=\"\">所以真正的问题是：当AI已经能写进论文，人类研究者还要写什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/polynoamial/status/1964464373516427491\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/polynoamial/status/1964464373516427491</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/emollick/status/1964447221853966775\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/emollick/status/1964447221853966775</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/ns123abc/status/1964724813940842934\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/ns123abc/status/1964724813940842934</a></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/SebastienBubeck/status/1958198661139009862\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/SebastienBubeck/status/1958198661139009862</a></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2509.03065\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2509.03065</a></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "GPT-5 首次以定理贡献者身份进入数学论文，引发了 AI 在科研中扮演新角色的热烈讨论，并对其原创性与博士培养影响提出担忧。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "GPT-5 首次以定理贡献者身份进入数学论文，引发了 AI 在科研中扮演新角色的热烈讨论，并对其原创性与博士培养影响提出担忧。",
  "summary": "文章详细报道了 GPT-5 首次作为“定理贡献者”出现在数学研究论文中的里程碑事件，解决了 Malliavin--Stein 框架下第四矩定理的收敛速度量化问题，标志着 AI 在基础数学研究领域的重大进展。然而，文章也深入揭示了 GPT-5 在推导过程中出现的错误，强调了人类研究者在引导、纠错和验证方面不可或缺的作用，凸显了“教授+AI”协同模式的重要性。文章进一步引用了 GPT-5 在凸优化领域取得突破的案例，同时指出 AI 的成果多依赖于对现有工具的快速复用，缺乏真正的原创性。最后，文章提出了对 AI 作为科研加速器可能带来的深远影响的担忧，包括“正确但平庸”成果的泛滥，以及对博士生研究直觉和批判性思维培养的潜在负面影响，引发了对未来人类研究者角色的深刻反思。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GPT-5 首次以定理贡献者身份进入数学论文，实现了基础数学研究的突破。",
      "explanation": "GPT-5 成功推导了第四矩定理的收敛速度，将定性收敛升级为定量收敛，对数学应用具有重要意义，标志着 AI 在解决复杂数学难题方面迈出了关键一步。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 在科研中并非独立完成，而是需要人类专家引导和纠错的“教授+AI”模式。",
      "explanation": "尽管 GPT-5 能快速生成证明，但其推导过程存在错误，凸显了人类在验证、修正和提供原创性洞察方面的不可替代性，强调了人机协同的重要性。"
    },
